## Dark Mode

Dark mode is automatic via `prefers-color-scheme`. Colors defined in [app/globals.css](mdc:app/globals.css) adjust automatically.

## TypeScript

- Always define prop interfaces
- Extend appropriate HTML element types when creating wrappers
- Use proper typing for event handlers and refs
